SLAKING spends all day lying down and
lolling about.
It eats grass growing within its reach. If it eats all the grass it can reach,
this POKMON reluctantly moves to
another spot.

Wherever SLAKING live, rings of over
a yard in diameter appear in grassy
fields. They are made by the POKMON as it eats all the grass within reach
while lying prone on the ground.

Hordes of SLAKING gather around trees
when fruits come into season. They wait
around patiently for ripened fruits to fall
out of the trees.

Monaflmit passe toute sa journe allong  paresser.
Il mange toute lherbe quil trouve  porte de main.
Ensuite, il change dendroit,  contrecur.

Letarking verbringt den Tag damit, herumzuliegen und nichts
zu tun. Es ernhrt sich von Gras, das in seiner Reichweite
wchst. Hat es alles aufgefressen, so sucht es sich widerwillig
ein anderes Pltzchen.

Slaking se pasa todo el da tumbado vagueando. Se come la
hierba que tiene a su alcance y, una vez que ha acabado con
ella, se va de mala gana a otro sitio.

Slaking passa tutto il giorno disteso pigramente, mangiando
lerba che cresce a portata di mano. Dopo aver esaurito
lerba vicino a s, si sposta controvoglia in un altro luogo.

On trouve parfois des cercles de plus de 1 m de rayon

par les Monaflmit qui passent leurs journes allongs
 manger toute lherbe  porte de main.

Wo dieses Letarking lebt, hinterlsst es Kreise von 1 m Radius
auf den Wiesen. Es frisst nmlich all das Gras, das in seiner
Reichweite wchst. Dabei liegt es buchlings auf dem Boden.

Cuando Slaking se instala a vivir en una zona, aparecen
crculos de un metro de radio de terreno baldo, pues se
come todo el csped que pilla mientras est tumbado boca
abajo.

Dove vive Slaking, si formano anelli del raggio di 1 m nei
prati erbosi. Infatti, quando questo Pokmon si stende
prono al suolo, mangia tutta lerba che riesce a raggiungere.

Wherever Slaking live, rings of over a yard in diameter appear
in grassy fields. They are made by the Pokmon as it eats all
the grass within reach while lying prone on the ground.
